en_647286_0	In another move of reconciliation and ethnic harmony, troops of the 593 Brigade under the 59 Division renovated a pre-school and its children's park and handed it over to the school authority on Tuesday (4) at Chemmali GN Division in Mullaittivu District.
en_647286_1	On the instructions of Major General Dushyantha Rajaguru, Commander, Security Forces - Mullaittivu (SF-MLT), troops of the 593 Brigade took the initiative under the direction of 593 Brigade Commander Colonel Lanka Amarapala with the blessings of Major General Ruwan Wanigasooriya, General Officer Commanding, 59 Division.
en_647286_2	Financial assistance for this commendable project was provided by Mr Thulanthan Senanayake a philanthropist.
en_647286_3	Major General Ruwan Wanigasooriya, General Officer Commanding, 59 Division graced the occasion as the Chief Guest along with Colonel Lanka Amarapala, 593 Brigade Commander, Mrs U Puwanaraja, Zonal Director Education Mullaittivu, Mr Gunapalan, Teaching Advisor for preschools, Mullaittivu, Mr S Baskaran, Principal, Chemmaili Maha Vidyalaya, Mr Thulantha Senanayake, Mrs Dilrukshi Senanayake and Mr Ranjith Attanayake, Regional Marketing Manager (CBL).
en_647286_4	Essential stationeries and Manchi gift packs were also distributed among children in the ceremony.
